      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-29/austin-is-grilled-by-lawmakers-on-his-secret-hospitalization</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 16:43:16 GMT</pubDate>
